{
  "name": "Nothing Escapes Us",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/sundries/gaming/chess-pawn-white-pink.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 17th level, your sensory techniques are unparalleled.</p><p>You are always under the effects of the Sensing Technique jutsu.</p><p>The effects of this jutsu cannot be negated or dispelled.</p><p>If a creature would enter the area of your Sensing Technique jutsu, you may take the Sense Chakra special action as a free action.</p><p>A creature cannot avoid detection from your Sense Chakra special action as long as they have one or more Chakra.</p><p>You may spend a Brave Order at no action cost.</p><p>Until the end of your next turn, all allies within 90 feet of you gain the same benefits of the Sensing Technique jutsu as you do, as if they had cast the jutsu.</p>",
